data.description: Quiet street in friendly neighborhood.  Home has an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace in great room and kitchen. The Primary bedroom has separation from other bedrooms, with walk in closet.  Laminate flooring in all main living areas.  Covered patio partially enclosed. Large paved RV parking area with full hook ups on side of home, 50amp service and clean out.  Great place for storing your large RVs.  2 Storage sheds. Spacious private fenced backyard.
